==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gummy
<hw>Gum"my</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Compar.
<er>Gummer</er> (<?/); superl. <er>Gummirst</er>.]</ety> <def>Consisting
of gum; viscous; adhesive; producing or containing gum; covered with gum
or a substance resembling gum.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Kindles the <qex>gummy</qex> bark of fir or pine.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Then rubs his <qex>gummy</qex> eyes.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Gummy tumor</b></col> <fld>(Med.)</fld>, <cd>a
gumma.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gump</ent>⟦br⟧
